<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.8.9">
<l>kaṭivār taṇṇantuḻāyk kaṇṇaṉviṇ ṇavarperumāṉ</l>
<l>paṭivā ṉamiṟanta paramaṉ pavittiraṉcīr</l>
<l>ceṭiyār nōykaḷkeṭap paṭintu kuṭaintāṭi</l>
<l>yaṭiyēṉ vāymaṭuttup parukik kaḷittēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kṛṣṇa with cool Tulsi overflowing with fragrance, the great lord of the celestials,</l>
<l>the highest who goes beyond earth [and] sky, the pure one’s excellence,</l>
<l>settling, working through, playing in [it] so that [my] sinful pains get lost,</l>
<l>I [his] servant put [it] in [my] mouth, drank [and] was exulted.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
